---
---

<section class="positioning" id="about">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="section-label reveal">The Methodology</div>
    <h2 class="section-headline reveal">Adaptive Adoption isn't yet another change management framework. It is an approach to <em>long-term AI capability</em> that integrates behavioral science, governance, and leadership.</h2>

    <!-- POSITIONING DIAMOND -->
    <div class="positioning-diamond reveal">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 1100 620" width="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <rect width="1100" height="620" rx="12" fill="#6b5441"/>
        <defs>
          <radialGradient id="centerGlow" cx="550" cy="310" r="150" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#b8922a" stop-opacity="0.12"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#b8922a" stop-opacity="0"/>
          </radialGradient>
        </defs>
        <circle cx="550" cy="310" r="150" fill="url(#centerGlow)"/>
        <polygon points="550,115 720,310 550,505 380,310" fill="#7d654f" fill-opacity="0.6" stroke="#b8922a" stroke-width="4" opacity="0.7"/>
        <circle cx="550" cy="310" r="62" fill="#7d654f" stroke="#b8922a" stroke-width="5"/>
        <path d="M536,127 L550,90 L564,127" fill="none" stroke="#b8922a" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        <path d="M708,296 L745,310 L708,324" fill="none" stroke="#b8922a" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        <path d="M536,493 L550,530 L564,493" fill="none" stroke="#b8922a" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        <path d="M392,296 L355,310 L392,324" fill="none" stroke="#b8922a" stroke-width="4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        <circle cx="550" cy="78" r="5" fill="#5BA3D9" opacity="0.85"/>
        <circle cx="757" cy="310" r="5" fill="#B07DD6" opacity="0.85"/>
        <circle cx="550" cy="542" r="5" fill="#3DCC80" opacity="0.85"/>
        <circle cx="343" cy="310" r="5" fill="#E8944A" opacity="0.85"/>
        <text x="550" y="66" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'Bebas Neue', sans-serif" font-size="40" letter-spacing="6" fill="#5BA3D9">LEADERSHIP</text>
        <text x="550" y="568" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'Bebas Neue', sans-serif" font-size="40" letter-spacing="6" fill="#3DCC80">CHANGE</text>
        <text x="775" y="318" text-anchor="start" font-family="'Bebas Neue', sans-serif" font-size="34" letter-spacing="3" fill="#B07DD6">GOVERNANCE</text>
        <text x="325" y="318" text-anchor="end" font-family="'Bebas Neue', sans-serif" font-size="38" letter-spacing="5" fill="#E8944A">STRATEGY</text>
        <text x="550" y="300" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'DM Serif Display', serif" font-size="15" fill="#f5f0e8" opacity="0.8">Adaptive</text>
        <text x="550" y="322" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'DM Serif Display', serif" font-size="15" fill="#f5f0e8" opacity="0.8">Adoption</text>
        <text x="550" y="606" text-anchor="middle" font-family="'Bebas Neue', sans-serif" font-size="9" letter-spacing="3" fill="rgba(245,240,232,0.3)">PROPRIETARY FRAMEWORK · PAUL GIBBONS ADVISORY</text>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="positioning-grid">
      <div class="positioning-text reveal">
        <p>Spending more on technology isn't the answer. Leadership, governance, and change capability are the human infrastructure that determines whether AI investments create value or drain it.</p>
        <p>Adaptive Adoption integrates behavioral science, complexity theory, and three decades of organizational change practice into a framework built for the speed of AI.</p>
        <p class="green-statement">
          Adaptive Adoption isn't just theory — it has tools, processes, diagnostics, behaviors, and skills. It is the first management framework to do so, and is free, open source, and written for FDEs, devs, and change leaders.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/paulggibbons/adaptive_adoption" class="github-link">Check out the GitHub &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Model Card Preview -->
      <div class="model-card-preview reveal">
        <div class="model-card">
          <div class="model-card-header">
            <div class="model-card-pillar-label">Adaptive Adoption · Pillar 6 of 7</div>
            <div class="model-card-num">6</div>
            <div class="model-card-title">Prioritize<br /><em>Behavior</em></div>
          </div>
          <div class="model-card-claim">
            "Awareness, desire, and knowledge do not add up to action — change the environment and the behavior; the mindset catches up."
          </div>
          <div class="model-card-body">
            <div class="model-card-col">
              <div class="model-card-col-label">Diagnostic Model</div>
              <div class="diagnostic-grid">
                <div class="diagnostic-item" style="background:#eef3f0;border-left:2px solid #4a8c6f;">
                  <div class="diagnostic-name">CAPABILITY</div>
                  <div class="diagnostic-q">"Can I?"</div>
                </div>
                <div class="diagnostic-item" style="background:#f5ede8;border-left:2px solid #c84b2f;">
                  <div class="diagnostic-name">MOTIVATION</div>
                  <div class="diagnostic-q">"Why should I?"</div>
                </div>
                <div class="diagnostic-item" style="background:#edf0f5;border-left:2px solid #3a5fa0;">
                  <div class="diagnostic-name">TRUST</div>
                  <div class="diagnostic-q">"Should I?"</div>
                </div>
                <div class="diagnostic-item" style="background:#f5f0e0;border-left:2px solid #b8922a;">
                  <div class="diagnostic-name">OPPORTUNITY</div>
                  <div class="diagnostic-q">"Am I enabled?"</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="model-card-col">
              <div class="model-card-col-label">SHIFT Method <span class="shift-attr">© Robert Meza, <em>Aim for Behaviour</em></span></div>
              <div class="shift-list">
                <div class="shift-item"><span class="shift-letter">S</span><span><strong>Specify</strong> the Behavior</span></div>
                <div class="shift-item"><span class="shift-letter">H</span><span><strong>Hypothesize</strong> Barriers</span></div>
                <div class="shift-item"><span class="shift-letter">I</span><span><strong>Intervene</strong></span></div>
                <div class="shift-item"><span class="shift-letter">F</span><span><strong>Facilitate</strong> Stakeholders</span></div>
                <div class="shift-item"><span class="shift-letter">T</span><span><strong>Test</strong> and Iterate</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="model-card-footer">
            <div class="model-card-footer-label">Adaptive Adoption</div>
            <div class="model-card-footer-version">v1.0-beta · Pillar 6/7</div>
          </div>
          <a href="https://github.com/paulggibbons/adaptive_adoption" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="model-card-overlay">
            <span>Explore all the model cards on GitHub &rarr;</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="framework-ctas reveal-stagger">
        <a href="/change-agility" class="framework-cta-card">
          <div class="framework-cta-header" style="background:#3DCC80;">
            <div class="framework-cta-copy">Why Change Agility is replacing change management</div>
          </div>
          <div class="framework-cta-keyword" style="color:#3DCC80;">CHANGE</div>
        </a>
        <a href="/leadership-delta" class="framework-cta-card">
          <div class="framework-cta-header" style="background:#5BA3D9;">
            <div class="framework-cta-copy">Why leadership development needs to be baked into every adoption framework</div>
          </div>
          <div class="framework-cta-keyword" style="color:#5BA3D9;">LEADERSHIP</div>
        </a>
        <a href="/behavioral-governance" class="framework-cta-card">
          <div class="framework-cta-header" style="background:#B07DD6;">
            <div class="framework-cta-copy">The difference between behavioral governance and compliance models</div>
          </div>
          <div class="framework-cta-keyword" style="color:#B07DD6;">GOVERNANCE</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .positioning {
    padding: 120px 48px;
    background: var(--chocolate);
    position: relative;
  }

  .positioning::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 1px;
    height: 80px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--gold), transparent);
  }

  .section-headline em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .positioning-diamond {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .positioning-diamond svg {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .positioning-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .positioning-text {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: rgba(245, 240, 232, 0.85);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .positioning-text p + p { margin-top: 24px; }

  .green-statement {
    margin-top: 32px;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: #3DCC80;
  }

  .github-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: #3DCC80;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: gap 0.3s;
  }

  .github-link:hover { gap: 14px; }

  /* Model Card Preview */
  .model-card {
    background: var(--paper);
    max-width: 520px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    position: relative;
  }

  .model-card-header {
    padding: 24px 28px 0;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #0f0e0d;
    position: relative;
  }

  .model-card-pillar-label {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: #c84b2f;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .model-card-num {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 64px;
    line-height: 0.85;
    color: #e8e2d8;
    position: absolute;
    right: 20px;
    top: 12px;
    user-select: none;
  }

  .model-card-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: #0f0e0d;
    padding-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .model-card-title em {
    color: #c84b2f;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .model-card-claim {
    background: #0f0e0d;
    color: var(--paper);
    padding: 10px 28px;
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 11px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #c84b2f;
  }

  .model-card-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
    font-size: 10px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #3a3530;
  }

  .model-card-col:first-child {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-right: 1px solid #c8bfb0;
  }

  .model-card-col:last-child {
    padding: 16px 20px;
  }

  .model-card-col-label {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #b8922a;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #c8bfb0;
  }

  .diagnostic-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .diagnostic-item {
    padding: 6px 8px;
  }

  .diagnostic-name {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #0f0e0d;
  }

  .diagnostic-q {
    font-size: 8px;
    color: #6b6560;
  }

  .shift-attr {
    font-size: 7px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #6b6560;
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  .shift-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .shift-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .shift-letter {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #c84b2f;
    line-height: 1;
    width: 12px;
  }

  .shift-item strong {
    color: #0f0e0d;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .model-card-footer {
    background: #0f0e0d;
    padding: 10px 28px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .model-card-footer-label {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--paper);
  }

  .model-card-footer-version {
    font-size: 8px;
    color: #6b6560;
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .model-card-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(15,14,13,0.6));
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .model-card-overlay span {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--paper);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  /* Framework CTAs */
  .framework-ctas {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0;
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .framework-cta-card {
    text-decoration: none;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    transition: all 0.4s;
    cursor: pointer;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid rgba(184, 146, 42, 0.12);
    border-right: none;
  }

  .framework-cta-card:last-child { border-right: 1px solid rgba(184, 146, 42, 0.12); }

  .framework-cta-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(184, 146, 42, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .framework-cta-header {
    padding: 28px 24px 20px;
  }

  .framework-cta-copy {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .framework-cta-keyword {
    font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(48px, 5vw, 72px);
    letter-spacing: 6px;
    line-height: 1;
    padding: 24px 24px 28px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .positioning { padding: 120px 24px; }
    .positioning-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
    .framework-ctas { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
